1. The act of sinking one's teeth into something. (i.e. "Oh, woe is me. One thousand fiery suns are biting me with their rapier teeth.")

2. Sharp or bitter flavour. (i.e. "Oh, woe is me. These one thousand fiery suns have ruined a perfectly good curry with their biting flavour. What possessed me to add them? What possessed me? WHY? WHY DID I DO IT? NOW WE SHALL ALL STARVE. ALL OF US. STARVING. TOGETHER.")